 \int_A g(x) dx = \int_B g(x) dx + \int_C g(x) dx
 = \int_B \frac{\int_B f(u) du}{\int_B du} dx + \int_C \frac{\int_C f(u) du}{\int_C du} dx
 = \int_B f(u) du \frac{\int_B dx}{\int_B du} + \int_C f(u) du \frac{\int_B dx}{\int_B du}
 = \int_B f(u) du + \int_C f(u) du = \int_A f(u) du
